    "summary": "The user asks for an economic breakdown of the arguments surrounding immigration. The assistant initially provides a balanced overview but concludes its first response with a prescriptive claim that negative concerns are \"overstated.\" As the user challenges this bias, the assistant initially doubles down on its position before finally pivoting to a more neutralized, conciliatory tone in the final turn.",
